Sept 2019 - Jun 2021 Mathematics Tutor

2012 Infinitesimal calculus for solutions to physics problems, SMBC patent 001




Jun 2022 - Sep 2022 Assistant Teacher | Karter Schools | Sterling, VA

Collaborated with other staff using a team approach. Demonstrated exceptional customer service to families and children by leading in specialized care for each student
Assisted in overseeing multiple special needs individuals
Provided support to all children. Oversaw individual and group activities such as personalized learning games and lesson material

May 2021 - Aug 2021 Shampoo Assistant | Salon Lofts | Sterling, VA

Developed advanced interpersonal skills and improved customers experience. Responsible for attending to all clients with friendly demeanor and outgoing personality
Created clean and organized salon environment. Provided clients with personal head massages along with shampoo process

Jul 2021 – Present Commissioned Artist | JenaveveOilPaintings | Remote

Single-handedly marketed and produced estimable Black and White portrait oil paintings
Analyzed proportions of individual facial features and backgrounds to recreate accurate representations on canvas
Committed over 40+ hours for each commissioned oil painting to refine technique and compose excellent product
